<ul><li> Done with Gill Man (<em>a.k.a.</em> The Creature from the Black Lagoon) in <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Pinball/MonsterBash" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Pinball/MonsterBash">Monster Bash</a></em>.
<div class="indent"><strong>Woman</strong>: "Wrap your flippers around me, fish-boy!"
